* A wrapper class for the crypto objects supported by BiometricPrompt and FingerprintManager.
 * Currently the framework supports {@link Signature}, {@link Cipher}, {@link Mac} and
 * {@link IdentityCredential} objects.
 * @hide

methods.name: public Signature getSignature()
methods.comment:
* Get {@link Signature} object.
     * @return {@link Signature} object or null if this doesn't contain one.

methods.name: public Cipher getCipher()
methods.comment:
* Get {@link Cipher} object.
     * @return {@link Cipher} object or null if this doesn't contain one.

methods.name: public Mac getMac()
methods.comment:
* Get {@link Mac} object.
     * @return {@link Mac} object or null if this doesn't contain one.

methods.name: public IdentityCredential getIdentityCredential()
methods.comment:
* Get {@link IdentityCredential} object.
     * @return {@link IdentityCredential} object or null if this doesn't contain one.

methods.name: public final long getOpId()
methods.comment:
* @hide
     * @return the opId associated with this object or 0 if none
